:{{Tag|1=ref name="foo"|2=open}}''content1''{{Tag|ref|close}}
:{{Tag|1=ref name="foo"|2=open}}''content2''{{Tag|ref|close}}
Only ''content1'' will show. refTools will catch this problem.

